data.description: Custom built, solid concrete block 3 bedroom, 2 bath home in the lovely low HOA community of Sebastian Crossings has many upgrades including a brand new gourmet kitchen with quartz countertops, plantation shutters, tile throughout, split bedrooms, garden tub in large master suite, breakfast nook, brick paver driveway and spacious inside laundry. Huge yard with lush landscaping and white vinyl fence. FL Rail Trail begins at front gate for walk/bike and canoe launch to river is right next door to community. Room for pool & HOA dues cover individual lawn maintenance! rmszappx&sub2err
